Niekto, koho miloval.

47
00:03:40,482 --> 00:03:42,211
Inak...

48
00:03:43,722 --> 00:03:47,021
Celú dobu mi to vŕta hlavou.

49
00:03:49,021 --> 00:03:52,061
Môžete mi o vašom 
bratovi povedať viac?

50
00:03:55,732 --> 00:03:57,732
