povedali predtým...

118
00:09:21,752 --> 00:09:24,292
Mali by sme sa vrátiť, je neskoro.

119
00:09:24,721 --> 00:09:26,091
Odkedy som asistentka pána Nama...

120
00:09:26,091 --> 00:09:27,492
