00:12:07,721 --> 00:12:09,351
Naozaj je to tak.

152
00:12:27,872 --> 00:12:28,872
Čo sa deje?

153
00:12:30,912 --> 00:12:32,711
Prestaň naňho myslieť.

154
00:12:32,711 --> 00:12:33,851
Preber sa, Yi Young.

155
00:12:39,252 --> 00:12:40,691
Muselo mi preskočiť.

156
00:12:41,122 --> 00:12:42,321
Preboha!

157
00:12:46,321 --> 00:12:47,762
