177
00:13:53,662 --> 00:13:54,662
Prosím?

178
00:13:55,132 --> 00:13:56,591
Zdravím, slečna Yang. Čo sa...

179
00:13:58,731 --> 00:13:59,731
Čo?

180
00:14:00,231 --> 00:14:01,902
