224
00:17:14,791 --> 00:17:17,402
Oni... Sú vonku...

225
00:17:17,562 --> 00:17:19,261
pred budovou.

226
00:18:20,122 --> 00:18:21,132
Slečna Hong.

227
00:18:22,491 --> 00:18:24,501
- Áno? 
- Počúvajte ma a natáčajte ďalej.

228
00:18:24,501 --> 00:18:25,531
Nepozerajte sa na mňa.

229
00:18:25,531 --> 00:18:27,701
Dobre.

230
00:18:27,701 --> 00:18:30,372
